data.title: Free Birthday Nutrition Facts PNG
data.meta_description: Free birthday nutritional facts label. Download our free birthday nutrition facts png file. Horizontal and Vertical format available.
data.text:
Searching for a birthday nutritional facts label to add to your chip bags, water bottle label, or candy wrapper party favors? You’re in luck! Grab our free birthday nutrition facts png to save time designing and give your favors a more authentic and personalized look!

Our free birthday nutritional facts labels include a vertical label and horizontal label. The vertical label is suitable for favors that are tall, such as chip bags, while the horizontal label is suitable for wide favors, such as chocolate bar wrappers or krispie treats.

The text on the label includes nutritional wording such as daily diet, daily value, and serving of food. Instead of different types of nutrients, the wording includes birthday wishes, gifts, fun & games, laughter and more.

How to Open Zipped Folder Download

Before you download, please note that these free birthday nutritional png labels are available to download in a zipped folder. In order to use the digital files in a zip folder, you must extract them. Depending on your device, there are different ways to do this.

If using a PC, right click the folder and select EXTRACT ALL. The computer will prompt you to save them somewhere on the device.

If using Apple products, simply double click the single zip file to extract the files.

Editable Nutrition Facts Label Template

If you would like a pre-designed or blank nutrition labels that you can edit instead, consider upgrading to our editable version. While you could purchase a SVG file, our png files in Canva or photoshop are much better as the text can be personalized to suit your event. You can edit it to say many different things, such as “Birthday Boy Nutrition Facts” or even make Birthday Girl Nutrition Facts labels. If you sell a physical item, you could also use this label for your business, such as custom homemade honey nutrition labels.
